# Top-level output/ subdirectory names to preserve across pipeline Stage 0
# "Clean Output Directories" runs. One name per line; blank lines and lines
# starting with # are ignored. Read by
# infrastructure.core.files.cleanup._load_output_preserve_manifest.
#
# This project's own test suite (tests/gate_support.py, documented in
# tests/AGENTS.md) treats output/data, output/figures, and output/reports as
# a committed golden-fixture snapshot the tests check against — not
# disposable pipeline output. A default pipeline run must not silently wipe
# them; set TEMPLATE_ACTIVE_INFERENCE_ALLOW_GATE_REBUILD=1 for an intentional
# refresh instead (see tests/AGENTS.md).
data
figures
reports
